title: DDFP 411: Week 14 preview & Hot Dog Bet payoff
itunes:title: DDFP 411: Week 14 preview & Hot Dog Bet payoff
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank and Matt "Money" Smith to make their Week 14 "Red Challenge Flag" picks. Also, the guys payoff Money's hot dog bet, discuss the Dolphins' throwback uniforms, and ask EmmaVP a series of exit interview questions. Plus, Shek introduces the newest "Mascot Matchup," where a Tampa Bay Buccaneer takes on a New Orleans Saint.
